      value: Barbarian Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[11].entryName
      value: Barbarian Pikeman
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[0].description
      value: The backbone of the Roman army. Clad in lorica segmentata and armed
        with a gladius and a heavy shield, they form an unbreakable wall of steel
        against barbarian hordes.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[1].description
      value: Deadly marksmen recruited from the provinces of the Empire. They rain
        down a lethal barrage of arrows on the enemy long before the barbarians can
        close the distance.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[2].description
      value: Disciplined warriors armed with long hastae. When they assume a defensive
        stance, their shield wall becomes certain death for any charging rider.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[3].description
      value: The pride of Rome. Swift and ruthless riders who flank the enemy, instantly
        tearing through enemy archer lines with their devastating charge.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[4].description
      value: A ruthless warrior from the northern tribes. Relies on brute strength
        rather than tactics.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[5].description
      value: Light barbarian cavalry patrolling the woods. Their goal is to bypass
        your legionaries and strike the rear to destroy archers and plunder the supply
        cart.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[6].description
      value: The heart of your army and the legion's deployment zone. Expanding the
        camp allows you to recruit more soldiers and unlocks access to elite unit
        types.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[7].description
      value: War is expensive, and legionaries don't fight for free. Capturing and
        upgrading a gold mine guarantees a steady flow of denarii during a siege.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[8].description
      value: A sturdy Roman watchtower mounted with a powerful ballista. It automatically
        fires armor-piercing bolts, providing crucial cover for your flanks.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[9].description
      value: Sharpened wooden logs driven deep into the earth. It is a basic but
        essential line of defense that holds back enemies and buys your troops time
        to regroup.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[10].description
      value: Attacks from afar using crude bows. Weak in melee but dangerous in groups.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: database.Array.data[11].description
      value: Uses long spears to stop horses. Very dangerous to your Cavalry units.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4124751948181047803, guid: 444c0dddcd3445143963ae88b685671e, type: 3}
