  - {fileID: 0}
  - {fileID: 0}
  guideMessages:
  - <b><color=#1E88E5>COMBAT:</color></b> Knights counter Archers. Spearmen deal
    <color=#E53935>x2 DMG</color> to Cavalry. Archers beat Spearmen.
  - <b><color=#FBC02D>ECONOMY:</color></b> Build a Mine early for passive Gold. Upgrade
    Barracks to unlock units and increase army cap.
  - <b><color=#43A047>DEFENSE:</color></b> Upgrade Castle HP and Tower DMG to survive
    longer. Crossbows provide heavy automated defense.
  - <b><color=#8E24AA>SKILLS:</color></b> Call the Supply Cart on cooldown for extra
    resources. Use Rain of Arrows to wipe out huge enemy waves.
  - <b><color=#00ACC1>META PROGRESSION:</color></b> Earn Gems by killing enemies.
    Spend them on permanent Talents in the Meta Shop.
